DJ Marcelle’s ‘BELP’s Shrinking Record Collection’ Mix

A three turntable mix of records recently given to me by my friend Sebastian, who runs the Jahmoni label and records under the name Belp.

I could (almost) freely pick from his vinyl collection. In return I mixed the records up in a two hour mix, often three vinyls playing at the same time.

1. Signature: PIL - Careering (Peel Session) (DJ Marcelle edit)
